iris
====

This repository serves as a personal collection of notes summarizing theoretical concepts in machine learning, robotics, the Standard Model of particle physics, electrical circuits, and electronic circuits.

The content is organized with the aim of concisely capturing key theoretical ideas based on multiple references. As a result, some sections may be challenging for beginners.

This material is intended solely as a personal memorandum. While care has been taken to ensure accuracy, completeness is not guaranteed.

I would also like to express my sincere gratitude to the many references that have contributed to the creation of this material.

Notes
-----

 * The content is subject to ongoing updates.
 * If you find any errors or issues, please feel free to report them via Issues or Pull Requests.

